{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "click-and-munch-api",
		"name": "ClickAndMunch API",
		"description": "Full API collection for the ClickAndMunch microservices backend.\n\n**Gateway:** http://localhost:8080\n\n**Services:**\n| Service | Port | Gateway Path |\n|---------|------|--------------|\n| AuthService | 8081 | /auth/** |\n| RestaurantService | 8082 | /restaurant/** |\n| GeoService | 8083 | (internal only) |\n| MenuService | 8084 | /menu/** |\n| OrderService | 8085 | /order/** |\n| ReservationService | 8086 | /reservation/** |\n| CheckoutService | 8089 | /checkout/** |\n\n**Flow:**\n1. Register a user\n2. Login to get a JWT token (auto-saved to `token` variable)\n3. Use protected Restaurant, Menu, Order, Reservation, and Checkout endpoints\n\n**Auth routes** are public. All other routes require a Bearer token.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "baseUrl",
			"value": "http://localhost:8080"
		},
		{
			"key": "token",
			"value": ""
		},
		{
			"key": "userId",
			"value": "1"
		},
		{
			"key": "restaurantId",
			"value": "1"
		},
		{
			"key": "locationId",
			"value": "1"
		},
		{
			"key": "categoryId",
			"value": ""
		},
		{
			"key": "itemId",
			"value": ""
		},
		{
			"key": "orderId",
			"value": "1"
		},
		{
			"key": "reservationId",
			"value": "1"
		},
		{
			"key": "customerId",
			"value": "1"
		}
	],
